---
name: openai-agent
description: Agent with tool calling for weather lookups
model:
  id: gpt-4o-mini
  provider: openai
  apiType: chat
  connection:
    kind: key
    apiKey: ${env:OPENAI_API_KEY}
  options:
    temperature: 0
    maxOutputTokens: 1024
inputs:
  - name: question
    kind: string
    default: What's the weather in Seattle?
tools:
  - name: get_weather
    kind: function
    description: Get the current weather for a city
    parameters:
      - name: city
        kind: string
        description: City name, e.g. "Seattle, WA"
        required: true
template:
  format:
    kind: jinja2
  parser:
    kind: prompty
---
system:
You are a helpful assistant with access to tools.
Use the get_weather tool when asked about weather.

user:
{{question}}
